		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/06/12/today-in-small-business-death-cafes/" data-title="Today in Small Business: Death Cafes" data-description="The importance of daydreaming. A guide to accepting credit cards. And how to make a commercial for local television.">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>The Economy</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ The United States posted a <a href="//www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-06-11/budget-deficit-in-u-s-narrows-as-economy-jobs-bolster-revenue.html">$130 billion budget deficit</a>Â in May and the smallest shortfall for the first eight months of a fiscal year since 2008.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Washington</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ The Chamber of Commerceâs <a href="//www.uschambersummit.com/">Small Business Summit</a> is under way in Washington.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ The Small Business Administration plans a <a href="//www.stardem.com/business/article_0d475e75-b67e-58eb-b5cb-4581df1312f2.html">crisis preparedness</a> webinar.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Eric Cantor&#8217;s loss is <a href="//www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/wonkblog/wp/2014/06/10/why-cantors-loss-is-especially-bad-news-for-big-business/">bad news</a> for big business.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Entrepreneurship</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here are 10 <a href="//www.entrepreneur.com/article/234689">counter-intuitive</a> pieces of advice from famous entrepreneurs.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ This is why daydreaming is <a href="//www.recruiter.co.uk/personal-dev/2014/06/why-daydreaming-is-an-essential-skill-for-business-owners/">an essential skill</a> for business owners. <span id="more-86308"></span></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Around the Country</b></p>
