<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Businesses in Texas <a href="//www.bizjournals.com/dallas/blog/2014/06/businesses-could-go-solar-without-any-upfront.html">can go solar</a> without any upfront costs using a new state program.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A Texas man hopes to <a href="//www.chron.com/news/houston-texas/article/Texas-man-hopes-to-turn-farm-disaster-into-vodka-5542353.php">turn a farm disaster</a> into a vodka success.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Philadelphia&#8217;s <a href="//www.bizjournals.com/philadelphia/blog/real-estate/2014/06/center-city-retail-scene-on-fire.html">retail scene is heating up</a>.</p>
