<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Capital One <a href="//www.marketwatch.com/story/a-first-for-major-banks-helping-customers-identify-potentially-unwanted-charges-2014-06-11?r">is piloting</a> a free service that can help small businesses identify unnoticed or unwanted charges.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ This is a guide for small businesses on <a href="//fitsmallbusiness.com/how-to-accept-credit-cards/">how to accept credit cards</a>.</p>
