<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Dentists</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A start-up <a href="//techcrunch.com/2014/06/11/weave-a-new-kind-of-telco-for-smbs-rings-up">has developed</a> a communications service for small and medium businesses but is first targeting dentists.</p>
