<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A <a href="//time.com/2850594/guys-your-smartphone-is-hurting-your-sperm/">new study</a> finds that the low-level electromagnetic radiation emitted by mobile devices lowers sperm motility by 8 percent and viability by 9 percent.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Hewlett-Packard is cooking up âambitious <a href="//www.businessweek.com/articles/2014-06-11/with-the-machine-hp-may-have-invented-a-new-kind-of-computer?">industrial-strength computing</a> technologyâ that, if and when itâs released, could replace a data centerâs worth of equipment with a single refrigerator-size machine.</p>
